OL,3,CMurder investigation as man stabbed to
OL,4,Cdeath in Westminster
OL,6,FA 26-year-old man was stabbed to death
OL,7,Fin Westminster on Friday night.
OL,9,FThe Metropolitan police has launched a
OL,10,Fmurder investigation after they were
OL,11,Fcalled to reports of a stabbing in
OL,12,FAbbey Orchard Street at 10.17pm.
OL,14,FOfficers found a man with stab wounds.
OL,16,FThey provided first aid before the
OL,17,FLondon Ambulance Service took him to a
OL,18,Fnearby hospital, where he was
OL,19,Fpronounced dead.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/4
