OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1774725064
OL,3,CMurder investigation as man stabbed to
OL,4,Cdeath in Westminster
OL,6,FThe man's next of kin have been
OL,7,Finformed and are being supported by
OL,8,Fspecialist officers.
OL,10,FNo arrests have been made.
OL,12,FDetective Superintendent Dean Lanfear
OL,13,Fsaid: "We understand the concern this
OL,14,Fincident may cause. Officers are on
OL,15,Fpatrol in the area to provide a visual
OL,16,Fdeterrent and to offer reassurance to
OL,17,Fresidents.
