OL,3,CMurder investigation as man stabbed to
OL,4,Cdeath in Westminster
OL,6,F"If anyone saw or has any information
OL,7,Fabout what happened last night, please
OL,8,Fcontact the police. Even the slightest
OL,9,Fbit of information can help."
OL,11,FA post-mortem examination will be held
OL,12,Fin due course, police said.
OL,14,FAnyone with information is asked to
OL,15,Fcall police on 101, quoting reference
OL,16,FCAD 8270/27MAR, or contact
OL,17,FCrimestoppers anonymously on 0800 555
OL,18,F111.
